    "description": "<br><br><strong>This Prologue is a limited version of the full game to stop waiting and jump into running your tech store already. Don't forget to wishlist the full game to continue your most fun experience of running your personal tech store.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069570/extras/ab1bc89c432df24d48454318e36820a3.poster.avif?t=1728584514\" width=591 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069570/extras/ab1bc89c432df24d48454318e36820a3.webm?t=1728584514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>&quot;Tech Shop Simulator:Prologue&quot;</strong> is a free version of game <strong>&quot;Tech Shop Simulator&quot;</strong><br><strong>Design your store</strong>, optimizing for both efficiency and aesthetics. Determine the best display for your tech gadgets, manage your aisles, and ensure a seamless shopping experience for your customers.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069570/extras/449793943367e96a91cff465ad8e32a9.poster.avif?t=1728584514\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069570/extras/449793943367e96a91cff465ad8e32a9.webm?t=1728584514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069570/extras/449793943367e96a91cff465ad8e32a9.mp4?t=1728584514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Order stock using an in-game computer</strong>. Unpack the latest tech gadgets, organize them in your storage room, and strategically place them on shelves and displays.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069570/extras/011da22946836849ce4a98692ee49b08.poster.avif?t=1728584514\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069570/extras/011da22946836849ce4a98692ee49b08.webm?t=1728584514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069570/extras/011da22946836849ce4a98692ee49b08.mp4?t=1728584514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Handle customer</strong> transactions by scanning items and making sure customers leave satisfied with their shopping and checkout experience.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069570/extras/7b09e74c934bf170e0e36686ad7bc25e.poster.avif?t=1728584514\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069570/extras/7b09e74c934bf170e0e36686ad7bc25e.webm?t=1728584514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069570/extras/7b09e74c934bf170e0e36686ad7bc25e.mp4?t=1728584514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>As you accumulate profits, consider reinvesting. </strong>Expand your store's physical space, upgrade interiors, and continually adapt to the evolving demands of the tech retail world.<br><br><strong>In &quot;Tech Shop Simulator&quot;, every decision matters.</strong> Will you rise to the occasion, transforming a modest tech store into a retail powerhouse, while balancing customer satisfaction and finances?",
